OL,3,CInquest finds neglect of unwell
OL,4,Cprisoner contributed to his death
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died in prison
OL,7,Fsay he shouldn't have died alone and
OL,8,Fnobody should be treated the way he
OL,9,Fwas.
OL,11,FWayne Bayley died on May 17 2022, six
OL,12,Fdays after he had been remanded to HMP
OL,13,FPentonville.
OL,15,FAn inquest found that neglect in
OL,16,Fprison contributed to his death.
