OL,3,CInquest finds neglect of unwell
OL,4,Cprisoner contributed to his death
OL,6,FLorraine Bailey, Wayne's cousin, said:
OL,7,F"Wayne passed away in 2022 and from
OL,8,Fthen up until now, it's been a
OL,9,Fstruggle to come to terms with him not
OL,10,Fbeing here."
OL,12,FHis aunt, Valda Bayley, added: "I kept
OL,13,Fsaying to myself, we were all at home
OL,14,Fthat evening, getting on with our life
OL,15,Fand he was actually dying on his own
OL,16,Fand it just doesn't seem right, but
OL,17,Fthat should happen.
