OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F404A1731767255
OL,3,CInquest finds neglect of unwell
OL,4,Cprisoner contributed to his death
OL,6,F"I don't think anybody should die on
OL,7,Ftheir own, really. But the fact that
OL,8,Fit happened to him, it's even more sad
OL,9,Fthat we didn't get to say bye...I
OL,10,Fdon't think anybody, nobody should
OL,11,Fhave to be treated that way or have to
OL,12,Fgo through that at all."
OL,14,FThe 43-year-old was found unresponsive
OL,15,Fin a cell on the healthcare unit in
OL,16,Fthe prison, 10 hours after he was
OL,17,Frestrained by prison officers after
OL,18,Fcomplaining about the condition of his
OL,19,Fcell.
