OL,3,CInquest finds neglect of unwell
OL,4,Cprisoner contributed to his death
OL,6,FHe had sickle cell disease, epilepsy
OL,7,Fand delusional disorder for which he
OL,8,Fwas taking medication.
OL,10,FHe was moved to a segregated cell and
OL,11,Fsubject to a forcible strip search
OL,12,Fwhich involved his clothes being cut
OL,13,Foff and being left naked for seven
OL,14,Fhours.
OL,16,FThe restraint that police had him
OL,17,Funder resulted in acute chest
OL,18,Fsyndrome, a complication caused by
OL,19,Fsickle cell disease.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/13
