OL,3,CInquest finds neglect of unwell
OL,4,Cprisoner contributed to his death
OL,6,FHe told staff at the prison that he
OL,7,Fcould not breathe, but his pleas were
OL,8,Fignored.
OL,10,FHis family say they're struggling to
OL,11,Fprocess the conclusion of the inquest.
OL,13,FValda continued: "We're left feeling
OL,14,Fnumb at the moment because after the
OL,15,Fday, after everything was finished,
OL,16,Fyou're lost... so if we can help to
OL,17,Fsave another family, make awareness so
OL,18,Fsomebody else doesn't have to go
OL,19,Fthrough, what then? Wayne didn't die
OL,20,Fin vain.
