OL,6,F"We don't want him to want it to be
OL,7,Fthat he died for nothing. So this is
OL,8,Fwhy we're doing this, because we want
OL,9,Fother people to know and if you don't
OL,10,Fagree with something, don't accept it.
OL,12,F"Push further and see. You need to get
OL,13,Fa proper answer, which is what we
OL,14,Fwanted."
