OL,3,CInquest finds neglect of unwell
OL,4,Cprisoner contributed to his death
OL,6,FThe nurse did not complete the initial
OL,7,Fassessment to determine whether Mr
OL,8,FBayley was fit to be segregated but
OL,9,Fsegregation officers thought she
OL,10,Fplanned later to do it. However, she
OL,11,Flater confirmed she was not going to
OL,12,Fdo it and that a mental health nurse
OL,13,Fshould do it, who then concluded he
OL,14,Fwas not fit for segregation.
OL,16,FThere was an arrangement for Wayne to
OL,17,Fbe moved to the inpatient unit but
OL,18,Fwhen he arrived he told staff he could
OL,19,Fnot breathe - it was around three
OL,20,Fhours later staff became concerned and
OL,21,Fhe was pronounced dead that night.
