OL,3,CInquest finds neglect of unwell
OL,4,Cprisoner contributed to his death
OL,6,FThe nurse responsible for monitoring
OL,7,Fhis physical health during and after
OL,8,Fthe restraint failed to address the
OL,9,Fworsening of his condition.
OL,11,FIn particular, she did not take vital
OL,12,Fobservations that an expert
OL,13,Fhaematologist considered would have
OL,14,Fconfirmed that the restraint had
OL,15,Ftriggered a sickle cell crisis. This
OL,16,Fwould have required urgent hospital
OL,17,Ftreatment which would have saved his
OL,18,Flife.
