OL,6,FLorraine added: "The emphasis at the
OL,7,Fend of the day is they are from
OL,8,FWayne's case.''
OL,10,F"They have things, they are putting
OL,11,Fthings into place. But what we want is
OL,12,Ffurther development of that, further
OL,13,Ftraining, further awareness and for
OL,14,Fthat to be replicated to nationally
OL,15,Fthrough all prisons, not just one
OL,16,Fprison.''
