OL,6,F"So yes, they're doing it at
OL,7,FPentonville, we heard that. But are
OL,8,Fthey doing it everywhere else? What
OL,9,Fare government doing to ensure that
OL,10,Fit's been done everywhere else?
OL,11,FBecause if the practices are good, it
OL,12,Fshould be replicated. And so for us
OL,13,Fit's wider. If something's good for
OL,14,Fone, then it should be good (for all)."
