OL,3,CInquest finds neglect of unwell
OL,4,Cprisoner contributed to his death
OL,6,FThe findings also included that the
OL,7,Finitial use of force was not justified
OL,8,Fand the lack of a healthcare
OL,9,Fprofessional when Wayne was moved was
OL,10,Fa missed opportunity. His request to
OL,11,Fsee a doctor was also not properly
OL,12,Ffollowed up.
OL,14,F"It's not just about sickle cell
OL,15,Fbecause people can have many long term
OL,16,Fillnesses in it that you can't see
OL,17,Fstraight away," continued Valda.
