OL,6,F"So if they put something like that in
OL,7,Fplace, no matter what it is, it will
OL,8,Fmake them aware. Okay, this person's
OL,9,Fgot 'xyz' so you can keep a closer eye
OL,10,Fand monitor them better than they are
OL,11,Fdoing now. So it's not just sickle
OL,12,Fcell...It could be anything."
OL,14,FA Prison Service spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"Our thoughts are with Mr Bayley's
OL,16,Ffamily and friends at this difficult
OL,17,Ftime.
