OL,6,F"Following Mr Bayley's death, we have
OL,7,Fimproved training for prison staff
OL,8,Faround the use of force and
OL,9,Fsegregation to ensure that prisoners
OL,10,Fand prison staff are kept safe. We
OL,11,Fwill respond to the Prevention of
OL,12,FFuture Deaths report in due course."
